---
import {
  MessageCircle,
  Mail,
  Linkedin,
  Instagram,
  Github,
  Music,
  ArrowRight
} from "lucide-astro";

const WHATSAPP =
  "https://wa.me/34650850163?text=Hola%20ByteZagal,%20quiero%20hablar%20sobre%20mi%20proyecto.";
const EMAIL = "contacto@bytezagal.es";

const serviceLinks = [
  { href: "/servicios/arreglos", label: "Rescate y arreglos" },
  { href: "/servicios/digitalizacion", label: "Digitalización" },
  { href: "/servicios/ecommerce", label: "Tiendas online" }
];

const socialLinks = [
  {
    href: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/pedro-aguilar-lopez-569533233/",
    label: "LinkedIn",
    icon: Linkedin
  },
  {
    href: "https://instagram.com/bytezagal",
    label: "Instagram",
    icon: Instagram
  },
    {
    href: "https://www.malt.es/profile/bytezagal",
    label: "Malt",
    icon: Github
  },
  {
    href: "https://www.tiktok.com/@bytezagal",
    label: "TikTok",
    icon: Music
  },
  {
    href: "https://github.com/ByteZagal",
    label: "GitHub",
    icon: Github
  }
];
---

<section id="contacto" class="relative py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4">
    <div
      class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white/95 shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/70 backdrop-blur"
      data-contact-card
    >
      <div class="grid gap-0 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.05fr)_minmax(0,0.95fr)]">
        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 p-8 sm:p-10 lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-slate-500" data-reveal>
            Contacto
          </p>

          <h2
            class="mt-3 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl"
            data-reveal
            data-reveal-delay="60"
          >
            Hablemos de lo que necesita tu negocio
          </h2>

          <p
            class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-slate-600 sm:text-lg"
            data-reveal
            data-reveal-delay="120"
          >
            Trabajo también en remoto para toda España.
            Si tu web está lenta, rota, desordenada o simplemente se ha quedado pequeña,
            vemos la vía más sensata: parche, refactor o reconstrucción parcial.
          </p>

          <div
            class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row"
            data-reveal
            data-reveal-delay="180"
          >
            <a
              href={WHATSAPP}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-700 px-5 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-emerald-900/10 transition hover:bg-emerald-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-emerald-700 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
              aria-label="Abrir conversación por WhatsApp"
            >
              <MessageCircle class="h-5 w-5" />
              Escribir por WhatsApp
            </a>

            <a
              href="/contratame"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-5 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-slate-400 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
            >
              Ver cómo trabajo
              <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4" />
            </a>
          </div>

          <div
            class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2"
            data-reveal
            data-reveal-delay="240"
          >
            {serviceLinks.map((link) => (
              <a
                href={link.href}
                class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 transition hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-white focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-slate-400 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
              >
                {link.label}
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 sm:p-10">
          <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="120">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-slate-500">
              Respuesta directa
            </p>

            <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
              También puedes escribirme por correo. Ahora mismo uso este buzón como canal principal.
            </p>

            <a
              href={`mailto:${EMAIL}`}
              class="mt-5 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 bg-slate-50 px-5 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-white focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-slate-400 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 sm:w-auto"
            >
              <Mail class="h-5 w-5" />
              {EMAIL}
            </a>
          </div>

          <div
            class="mt-8 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/80 p-5"
            data-reveal
            data-reveal-delay="200"
          >
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">
              Qué suelo resolver
            </h3>

            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
              <li>Web lenta o con errores que frenan negocio.</li>
              <li>SEO técnico flojo o estructura mal planteada.</li>
              <li>Necesidad de ordenar presencia, captación y operación.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div
            class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3"
            data-reveal
            data-reveal-delay="280"
          >
            {socialLinks.map((social) => (
              <a
                href={social.href}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 transition hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-slate-400 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
                aria-label={social.label}
              >
                <social.icon class="h-4 w-4" />
                {social.label}
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>

          <p
            class="mt-8 text-xs leading-6 text-slate-500"
            data-reveal
            data-reveal-delay="340"
          >
            Tus datos no se almacenan aquí. El mensaje se envía directamente a mi correo o WhatsApp
            y se trata conforme al <strong>RGPD</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    #contacto [data-reveal] {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(8px);
    }

    #contacto .reveal-in {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
      transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      #contacto .reveal-in {
        transition: none !important;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      const els = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll("#contacto [data-reveal]"));

      if (!("IntersectionObserver" in window) || els.length === 0) {
        els.forEach((el) => el.classList.add("reveal-in"));
        return;
      }

      const io = new IntersectionObserver(
        (entries) => {
          entries.forEach((entry) => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              const delay = parseInt(entry.target.getAttribute("data-reveal-delay") || "0", 10);
              setTimeout(() => entry.target.classList.add("reveal-in"), delay);
              io.unobserve(entry.target);
            }
          });
        },
        { threshold: 0.12 }
      );

      els.forEach((el) => io.observe(el));
    })();
  </script>
</section>
